# NOTE: This file ensures consistent line endings across Windows, macOS,
#       and Linux, preventing `git status` issues from CRLF/LF differences.
#       `* text=auto` normalizes text file line endings to LF in the repo
#       and converts to native OS on checkout. Explicitly marking file types
#       as `text` guarantees correct normalization, vital for cross-OS
#       development and avoiding spurious modifications.
* text=auto

# Ansible files
*.yml text
*.yaml text

# Scripts
*.sh text
*.ps1 text

# Configuration files
*.cfg text
*.ini text

# Vimscript
*.vim text

# Documentation
*.md text
*.txt text
